[[File:Bevel_Lemelisk-DSOTM.png|thumb|250px|Bevel Lemelisk, Master of Imperial Projects]]
The '''Master of Imperial Projects''' was the title held by the chief [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]], who headed the development and production of new Imperial technology. [[Bevel Lemelisk]] held this position during the height of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]]; after the destruction of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|First Death Star]], it was given to [[Umak Leth]].

